  "detailed_description": "Friendly Snowball is a fun multiplayer PVP ball game, to enjoy with friends.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Prepare for a slippery battle where you hit frosty balls with your giant hammer to score.<br></li><li>Use power ups scattered throughout the arena to help you beat the opponent team.<br></li><li>Play with friends and have fun in a snowy environment!</li></ul><br>Friendly Snowball is the first physic-based multiplayer game made with Playcraft!<br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "Friendly Snowball is a fun multiplayer PVP ball game, to enjoy with friends.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Prepare for a slippery battle where you hit frosty balls with your giant hammer to score.<br></li><li>Use power ups scattered throughout the arena to help you beat the opponent team.<br></li><li>Play with friends and have fun in a snowy environment!</li></ul><br>Friendly Snowball is the first physic-based multiplayer game made with Playcraft!<br><br>",
